benches-1.Name: Petite Stool
benches-1.Body:
This small teak root bench is a true gem from Indonesia. Crafted from reclaimed teak root, it's a tiny piece of art that packs a big punch. Its unique shape and intricate details make it a magical addition to any space.

Imagine this: you're walking through a lush garden, surrounded by vibrant flowers and towering trees. As you round a corner, you spot this petite cutie of a bench. It's like nothing you've ever seen before - its curves and twists seem to defy gravity, as if it were grown rather than crafted.

As you approach, you notice the intricate details of the teak root. The knots and twists tell a story of resilience and strength, of a tree that has weathered countless storms and emerged even more beautiful for it. And as you take a seat on this tiny bench, you feel a connection to the earth and the natural world around you.

This bench may be small, but it's mighty in its beauty and magic. It's a reminder that even the tiniest things can have a big impact on our lives. So if you're looking for a piece of art that's both functional and enchanting, look no further than this small teak root bench from Indonesia. It's sure to bring a touch of whimsy and wonder to your home or garden.

Picture this: you're sitting on your front porch, sipping a cup of coffee, and admiring the beauty of nature around you. Suddenly, your eye catches a glimpse of this stunning bench. It's made from a reclaimed teak root, giving it a rustic, earthy feel that perfectly complements its natural surroundings. And with enough room for one, it's the perfect spot to sit and reflect on the beauty of the world around you.

But this bench isn't just a functional piece of furniture - it's a conversation starter. Your guests will be amazed by its unique design and the story behind its creation. And as you sit on this bench, you'll feel a connection to the earth and the history of the teak root it was made from.

buddhas.Name: Ayesha Rainbow
buddhas.Body:
This 5-foot-tall Ayesha Buddha is a playful and colorful masterpiece, perfect for those who love to add a touch of fun and whimsy to their space. The drips of paint in bright, Crayola-like colors give it a sense of joy and lightheartedness, like a burst of confetti on a sunny day.

As you gaze upon this stunning work of art, you can't help but feel a sense of energy and excitement wash over you. The rainbow colors seem to dance and swirl across the surface, like a vibrant kaleidoscope that fills the air around you.

And as you look closer, you notice the intricate details of the dripped paint. Each color seems to have a life of its own, like a playful and mischievous character in a storybook. All the playful colors evoke the sweetness of a juicy piece of candy.

This rainbow-colored Ayesha Buddha is more than just a work of art - it's a celebration of life and all its vibrant colors. So if you're looking for a piece that will bring a smile to your face every time you see it, look no further. It's sure to become the centerpiece of any room, and a beloved treasure for years to come.

decor.Name: Ayesha Rainbow
decor.Body:
This 5-foot-tall Ayesha Buddha is a playful and colorful masterpiece, perfect for those who love to add a touch of fun and whimsy to their space. The drips of paint in bright, Crayola-like colors give it a sense of joy and lightheartedness, like a burst of confetti on a sunny day.

As you gaze upon this stunning work of art, you can't help but feel a sense of energy and excitement wash over you. The rainbow colors seem to dance and swirl across the surface, like a vibrant kaleidoscope that fills the air around you.

And as you look closer, you notice the intricate details of the dripped paint. Each color seems to have a life of its own, like a playful and mischievous character in a storybook. All the playful colors evoke the sweetness of a juicy piece of candy.

This rainbow-colored Ayesha Buddha is more than just a work of art - it's a celebration of life and all its vibrant colors. So if you're looking for a piece that will bring a smile to your face every time you see it, look no further. It's sure to become the centerpiece of any room, and a beloved treasure for years to come.

40" wide by 32" deep by 61" high.

living-room.Name: Petite Stool
living-room.Body:
This small teak root bench is a true gem from Indonesia. Crafted from reclaimed teak root, it's a tiny piece of art that packs a big punch. Its unique shape and intricate details make it a magical addition to any space.

Imagine this: you're walking through a lush garden, surrounded by vibrant flowers and towering trees. As you round a corner, you spot this petite cutie of a bench. It's like nothing you've ever seen before - its curves and twists seem to defy gravity, as if it were grown rather than crafted.

As you approach, you notice the intricate details of the teak root. The knots and twists tell a story of resilience and strength, of a tree that has weathered countless storms and emerged even more beautiful for it. And as you take a seat on this tiny bench, you feel a connection to the earth and the natural world around you.

This bench may be small, but it's mighty in its beauty and magic. It's a reminder that even the tiniest things can have a big impact on our lives. So if you're looking for a piece of art that's both functional and enchanting, look no further than this small teak root bench from Indonesia. It's sure to bring a touch of whimsy and wonder to your home or garden.

As you gaze upon this stunning work of art, you can't help but feel a sense of energy and excitement wash over you. The rainbow colors seem to dance and swirl across the surface, like a vibrant kaleidoscope that fills the air around you.

And as you look closer, you notice the intricate details of the dripped paint. Each color seems to have a life of its own, like a playful and mischievous character in a storybook. All the playful colors evoke the sweetness of a juicy piece of candy.

This rainbow-colored Ayesha Buddha is more than just a work of art - it's a celebration of life and all its vibrant colors. So if you're looking for a piece that will bring a smile to your face every time you see it, look no further. It's sure to become the centerpiece of any room, and a beloved treasure for years to come.

living-room.Name: Tonga Bench
living-room.Body:
This small bench made from rustic, reclaimed teak root is a true work of art. Handcrafted in Indonesia, this one-of-a-kind piece is sure to turn heads and capture hearts.

Picture this: you're sitting on your front porch, sipping a cup of coffee, and admiring the beauty of nature around you. Suddenly, your eye catches a glimpse of this stunning bench. It's made from a reclaimed teak root, giving it a rustic, earthy feel that perfectly complements its natural surroundings. And with enough room for one, it's the perfect spot to sit and reflect on the beauty of the world around you.

But this bench isn't just a functional piece of furniture - it's a conversation starter. Your guests will be amazed by its unique design and the story behind its creation. And as you sit on this bench, you'll feel a connection to the earth and the history of the teak root it was made from.

So if you're looking for a truly special piece to add to your home or outdoor space, look no further than this small bench made from rustic, reclaimed teak root. It's a piece of art that's sure to bring joy and wonder to your life.

new-arrivals.Name: Petite Stool
new-arrivals.Body:
This small teak root bench is a true gem from Indonesia. Crafted from reclaimed teak root, it's a tiny piece of art that packs a big punch. Its unique shape and intricate details make it a magical addition to any space.

Imagine this: you're walking through a lush garden, surrounded by vibrant flowers and towering trees. As you round a corner, you spot this petite cutie of a bench. It's like nothing you've ever seen before - its curves and twists seem to defy gravity, as if it were grown rather than crafted.

As you approach, you notice the intricate details of the teak root. The knots and twists tell a story of resilience and strength, of a tree that has weathered countless storms and emerged even more beautiful for it. And as you take a seat on this tiny bench, you feel a connection to the earth and the natural world around you.

This bench may be small, but it's mighty in its beauty and magic. It's a reminder that even the tiniest things can have a big impact on our lives. So if you're looking for a piece of art that's both functional and enchanting, look no further than this small teak root bench from Indonesia. It's sure to bring a touch of whimsy and wonder to your home or garden.

As you gaze upon this stunning work of art, you can't help but feel a sense of energy and excitement wash over you. The rainbow colors seem to dance and swirl across the surface, like a vibrant kaleidoscope that fills the air around you.

And as you look closer, you notice the intricate details of the dripped paint. Each color seems to have a life of its own, like a playful and mischievous character in a storybook. All the playful colors evoke the sweetness of a juicy piece of candy.

This rainbow-colored Ayesha Buddha is more than just a work of art - it's a celebration of life and all its vibrant colors. So if you're looking for a piece that will bring a smile to your face every time you see it, look no further. It's sure to become the centerpiece of any room, and a beloved treasure for years to come.

Imagine this: you're walking through a lush garden, surrounded by vibrant flowers and towering trees. As you round a corner, you spot this petite cutie of a bench. It's like nothing you've ever seen before - its curves and twists seem to defy gravity, as if it were grown rather than crafted.

As you approach, you notice the intricate details of the teak root. And as you take a seat on this tiny bench, you feel a connection to the earth and the natural world around you.

This bench may be small, but it's mighty in its beauty and magic. It's a reminder that even the tiniest things can have a big impact on our lives. unique-rare-finds.Name: Bodhi Buddha Head

wall-art.Body: Our Galicia Mirror has arrived measuring 40" wide by 51 1/2" high. This industrial look mirror is a mosaic of metal and iron fittings, tools and chains. Each one unique, we have them in stock , from India.
